<h2 id="lists-and-registers">Lists and registers</h2>

<p>We publish lists and registers of <abbr title="Animal and Plant Health Agency">APHA</abbr> approved premises related to animal health and welfare, and plant and seed information. Examples include:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/animal-by-product-operating-plants-approved-premises">approved animal by-product operating plants</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/finishing-units-for-cattle-approved-premises">finishing units for cattle</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/tse-testing-of-fallen-cattle-approved-premises">TSE testing of fallen cattle</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/poultry-health-scheme-list-of-members">Poultry Health Scheme: list of members</a></li>
</ul>

